{"id":2630,"date":"2023-08-19T16:00:41","date_gmt":"2023-08-19T09:00:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2630"},"modified":"2023-09-20T13:02:23","modified_gmt":"2023-09-20T06:02:23","slug":"giac-mo-dai-hoc-hoan-thanh-cac-tan-khoa-chinh-thuc-roi-to-chap-canh-cho-nhung-uoc-mo-xa","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/giac-mo-dai-hoc-hoan-thanh-cac-tan-khoa-chinh-thuc-roi-to-chap-canh-cho-nhung-uoc-mo-xa\/","title":{"rendered":"&#8220;GI\u1ea4C M\u01a0&#8221; \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC HO\u00c0N TH\u00c0NH, C\u00c1C T\u00c2N KHOA CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C \u201cR\u1edcI T\u1ed4\u201d CH\u1eaeP C\u00c1NH CHO NH\u1eeeNG \u01af\u1edaC M\u01a0 XA"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u1ef9 s\u01b0, C\u1eed nh\u00e2n, D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 <\/span> t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi m\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 v\u00e0 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc c\u00e1c T\u00e2n khoa tung m\u0169 l\u00ean tr\u1eddi mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ea3 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, bu\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o sinh vi\u00ean v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Trong kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed h\u00e2n hoan, t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o xen l\u1eabn x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng, s\u00e1ng nay 18\/08, c\u00e1c T\u00e2n K\u1ef9 s\u01b0, C\u1eed nh\u00e2n, D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5m b\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 v\u1eeba l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea7y n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o to l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u00eau h\u00e3nh c\u1ee7a Th\u1ea7y c\u00f4, Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-17375\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_0366-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a TS. Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00fay V\u00e2n &#8211; Ph\u00f3 Hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng, PGS.TS. \u0110\u00e0o Th\u1ecb \u00c1i Thi &#8211; Ph\u00f3 Hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng, c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 Tr\u01b0\u1edfng\/Ph\u00f3 Ph\u00f2ng ban, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng\/Ph\u00f3 c\u00e1c Khoa c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4, Qu\u00fd Ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 &#8211; c\u00e1c T\u00e2n khoa.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17373\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17373\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-17373 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_0065-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17373\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">TS. Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00fay V\u00e2n &#8211; Ph\u00f3 Hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng trao b\u1eb1ng khen cho c\u00e1c T\u00e2n K\u1ef9 s\u01b0, C\u1eed nh\u00e2n, D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eefng n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1, nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, nh\u1eefng b\u00f3 hoa t\u01b0\u01a1i th\u1eafm v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 h\u00e0nh trang c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh mang \u0111\u1ebfn L\u1ec5 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p 2023 d\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ebfn cho con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c \u201cgi\u1ea5c m\u01a1\u201d \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh hay c\u00e1c T\u00e2n khoa \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 1 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i, mang tr\u00ean vai nh\u1eefng tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng. Gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat nh\u00ecn con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean b\u1ee5c vinh danh nh\u1eadn B\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17385\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17385\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-17385 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_0136-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17385\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">PGS.TS. \u0110\u00e0o Th\u1ecb \u00c1i Thi &#8211; Ph\u00f3 Hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edfng trao b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c T\u00e2n khoa<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i L\u1ec5, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho c\u00e1c T\u00e2n khoa, c\u00f4 sinh vi\u00ean Khoa Du l\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef, Ph\u1ea1m Th\u1ecb M\u1ef9 H\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u00e1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 v\u1edbi bao k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u00f9ng Th\u1ea7y C\u00f4, b\u1ea1n b\u00e8.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_17389\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-17389\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-large wp-image-17389\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_9970-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-17389\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Ph\u1ea1m Th\u1ecb M\u1ef9 H\u1ea1nh \u2013 Sinh vi\u00ean l\u1edbp D108K11 Khoa Du l\u1ecbch &#8211; Ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef chia s\u1ebb t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i L\u1ec5<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ef9 H\u1ea1nh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ebfn Th\u1ea7y C\u00f4, Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng &#8211; n\u01a1i l\u01b0u gi\u1eef thanh xu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a bao th\u1ebf h\u1ec7: <em>&#8220;T\u1ee5c ng\u1eef c\u00f3 c\u00e2u \u201cKh\u00f4ng th\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ed1 m\u00e0y l\u00e0m n\u00ean\u201d. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi d\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a Th\u1ea7y C\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111em t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng qu\u00fd b\u00e1u ch\u1eafp c\u00e1nh cho ch\u00fang em tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1eddi sau n\u00e0y. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 t\u1eadn t\u1ee5y, s\u1ef1 \u00e2n c\u1ea7n d\u00ecu d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang em t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. Thay m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean, em xin g\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u1ea7y, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 t\u1ea5m l\u00f2ng tri \u00e2n, bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u00e0 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng&#8221;.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u1ea3m \u01a1n b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng con trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i \u0111\u00e8n s\u00e1ch v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 h\u00f4m nay ngay t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a con, b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n con mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng: \u201cB\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 \u01a1i con \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ed3i, con y\u00eau b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9!\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-17377 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/IMG_9687-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 xin g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c T\u00e2n K\u1ef9 s\u01b0, C\u1eed nh\u00e2n, D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c tri th\u1ee9c, m\u1edf ra c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda &#8220;sau \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc&#8221; \u0111\u1ea7y th\u00fa v\u1ecb. M\u1ebfn ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd r\u1eb1ng, gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean b\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn t\u1ea5m b\u1eb1ng danh gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat m\u00e0 h\u00f4m nay, m\u00e3i \u0111\u1ebfn sau n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 tr\u1ea3i qua bao nhi\u00eau vinh quang hay ch\u00f4ng gai, th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y ghi d\u1ea5u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1eadm trong k\u00fd \u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u2207 L\u01b0u l\u1ea1i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u1ea1i <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/u\/4\/folders\/1vbrxjiimLCmX1j1cDDsvJr821f_tTbjt\"><strong>L\u1ec5 T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p 2023<\/strong><\/a> nh\u00e9 Thadoers \u01a1i!!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i \u00f4m \u1ea5m \u00e1p v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00f3 hoa t\u01b0\u01a1i th\u1eafm t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n quen trao tay l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, l\u00e0 c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9: Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Hotline: 0934 07 8668 \u2013 0243 386 1601<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Website: <\/i><\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/\"><b><i>https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/<\/i><\/b><\/a><b><i>\u00a0<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Fanpage: <\/i><\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\"><b><i>https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo<\/i><\/b><\/a><\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng K\u1ef9 s\u01b0, C\u1eed nh\u00e2n, D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi m\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 v\u00e0 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc c\u00e1c T\u00e2n khoa tung m\u0169 l\u00ean tr\u1eddi mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ea3 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2504,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[36,1],"tags":[108,42,40],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2630"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2630"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2630\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2631,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2630\/revisions\/2631"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2504"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2630"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.ed